Package swinghelper

Annotation Type RestrictedMerger

@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target({TYPE,METHOD})
public @interface RestrictedMerger
Allows to prevent the SwingManager copying certain properties from the dummy JFrame to the processing window or turn off the icon or title of the original window to be kept.
Author:
NumericPrime

  • Optional Element Summary

    Optional Elements 
    Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
    boolean delete_old
    When set to false:
    This prevents the dummy JFrame to be deleted
    boolean override_generated
    When set to false:
    This prevents the dummy JFrame being overridden by the processing window after tranfering the data
    boolean transfer_data
    This prevents automaticly copying the dummy-window to the processing window.
    boolean transfer_icon  
    boolean transfer_name  
    boolean transfer_size
